    <detaileddescription>
<para>Checks if the scaling mode settings of the display are changed.</para>
<para><heading level="2">Syntax </heading>
</para>
<para><preformatted>
 adlx_bool    IsScalingModeChanged ()
 </preformatted></para>
<para><heading level="2">Parameters </heading>
</para>
<para>N/A</para>
<para><heading level="2">Return Value </heading>
</para>
<para>If the scaling mode settings are changed, <bold>true</bold> is returned.<linebreak/>
 If the scaling mode settings are not changed, <bold>false</bold> is returned.</para>
<para><heading level="2">Additional Info </heading>
</para>
<para><bold>Note:</bold> To obtain the display, use <ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_display_settings_changed_event__get_display" kindref="compound">GetDisplay</ref>.</para>
